---
title: Italian Sausage and Baby Broccoli Pasta with Oregano Gremolata and Parmesan Cheese
description: What’s not to love about the combination of sausage, baby broccoli, pasta, and creamy Parmesan? It’s an old-school Italian favorite that never gets old in the HelloFresh kitchen. And now, by cooking your pasta and broccoli in the same pot, it’s easier than ever!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-italian-sausage-and-baby-b-5145d7c5.jpg
